full_text: Screened by NARA, 2/10/2023 AUG 29 1975 This lady is the Mother in how of Namyen LANH who is the son of NEWYEN Hien who here presented corrupondone date Newten lug 20, 1975 from his blood uster THI CHIEN and her husband TRAN New who are refugeed located in Comp 3, tent 47, thing Predition REDuile
